SubString.CExoString: Asabis are desert-dwelling reptilian humanoids who are often found as mercenaries or slaves in the service of evil creatures. The average asabi male stands nearly seven feet tall, and their thick, pebbly skin is brown or gray in hue. They have yellow, egg-shaped eyes with horizontal slit pupils.
